lead_paragraph: Coco Crisp and Khris Davis got Oakland off to a quick start against Yu Darvish. Then came their big blows against a hard-throwing reliever to clinch the fourth series in a row for the Athletics.

headline.print_headline: Davis Homers Twice, Crisp Goes Deep as A's Beat Rangers 6-4
headline.main: Davis Homers Twice, Crisp Goes Deep as A's Beat Rangers 6-4
